		<description>
			<p>Also at 3rd level, you become unusually hardy against the foulest of demons and devils. You have resistance to poison damage dealt by fiends, and you have advantage on any saving throws against poison which fiends force you to make.</p>
			<p class="indent">Once you reach 15th level, you have advantage on any Constitution saving throw you make against a spell or ability of a fiend.</p>
