		<description>
			<p>At 13th level, you learn how to send fiends back to their pits. When you hit a fiend with a weapon attack, you can cast banishment on that fiend as a bonus action without using any components. The save DC for this spell is equal to 8 + your Intelligence modifier + your proficiency bonus.</p>
			<p class="indent">Once you use this ability, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p>
		</description>
